The elasticsearch 5 docs shows a snippet for the scroll parameter, where it is clearly a string  of duration

```
var allTitles = [];

// first we do a search, and specify a scroll timeout
client.search({
  index: 'myindex',
  // Set to 30 seconds because we are calling right back
  scroll: '30s',
  search_type: 'scan',
  fields: ['title'],
  q: 'title:test'
```

